A photorealistic aerial view of a dense Singapore HDB housing estate at golden hour, showing clusters of tall residential apartment blocks with distinctive colorful rooftops in blue, purple, and terracotta red, surrounded by tropical greenery and palm trees, with elevated MRT train tracks curving through the neighborhood in the distance, warm sunlight casting long shadows across the urban landscape, a single red circle of light hovering near the fourth floor of one prominent building as if marking a specific window, the scene capturing the organized yet vibrant character of Singapore public housing with its mix of schools, markets, and transit infrastructure nestled together.
